{
  "texts": [
    "All methods were carried out in accordance with relevant guidelines and regulations.",
    "Our data collection was approved by the University of Wisconsin-Madison Institutional Review Board (IRB) (#2021-1526).",
    "Informed consent was obtained from all of our participants.",
    "We adopted Generative Pre-trained Transformer 3 (GPT-3) from OpenAI as the language generator for our chatbot when we conducted our auditing study from December 2021 to February 2022.",
    "OpenAI's GPT-3 is an autoregressive language model family that is capable of human-like text completion tasks and these tasks can be tweaked to generate conversations."
  ]
}